name: NSData.CompressionAlgorithm
desc: An algorithm that indicates how to compress or decompress data.

items.name: case lz4
items.desc: The LZ4 compression algorithm, recommended for fast compression.

items.name: case lzfse
items.desc: The LZFSE compression algorithm, recommended for use on Apple platforms.

items.name: case lzma
items.desc: The LZMA compression algorithm, recommended for high-compression ratio.

items.name: case zlib
items.desc: The zlib compression algorithm, recommended for cross-platform compression.
